io.mosip.registration.device.scanner.wia

Enum WiaPropertyType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WiaPropertyType>
      • io.mosip.registration.device.scanner.wia.WiaPropertyType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com4j.ComEnum, Serializable, Comparable<WiaPropertyType>

    public enum WiaPropertyType
extends Enum<WiaPropertyType>
implements com4j.ComEnum

    The WiaPropertyType enumeration specifies the type of the value of an item property. Item properties can be found in the Properties collection of a Device or Item object.
